Class MissingFromMath2

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.dataset.internal.utils.MissingFromMath2

  • public class MissingFromMath2
extends java.lang.Object
    A few methods are missing in math vs math3, these are implemented in MissingFromMath2. At the point that math3 is upgraded, change the dependencies, re-write the methods within this class and inline them.
